subtests.name: URL matching of CSP should be done based on the subresource URL, not on the bundle URL, when the subresource URL is HTTPS URL.
URL matching of script-src CSP should be done based on the bundle URL when the subresource URL is urn:uuid: URL.
URL matching of frame-src CSP should be done based on the bundle URL when the frame URL is urn:uuid: URL.
URL matching of script-src CSP should be done based on the bundle URL when the subresource URL is uuid-in-package: URL.
URL matching of frame-src CSP should be done based on the bundle URL when the frame URL is uuid-in-package: URL.
